<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/36374066-one-day-closer"><img alt="One Day Closer: A Mother&#39;s Quest to Bring Her Kidnapped Daughter Home" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1508349928l/36374066._SX98_.jpg" />
